  "title": "Training Provided - Administrator / Admin Assistant (Dental Lab)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2,000 - $2,800 + AWS + VB</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Ubi</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working Days: 5.5 days </strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours: 8:30 am - 6.00pm / 8:30 am - 12:30pm</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Administrative Tasks:</strong> Generate sales orders and invoices, manage paperwork, and input data into the company system.</li>\n  <li><strong>Document Management:</strong> Organize and maintain physical and digital files.</li>\n  <li><strong>Office Management:</strong> Monitor and restock office supplies and inventory.</li>\n  <li><strong>Operations Oversight:</strong> Track deadlines to ensure cases are completed, packed, and dispatched on time.</li>\n  <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Serve as a point of contact for internal and external communications. Professionally respond to emails, calls, and messages.</li>\n  <li><strong>Packing &amp; Dispatch:</strong> Verify that all case components, lab-fabricated items, and required paperwork are included before shipping.</li>\n  <li><strong>Courier Coordination:</strong> Arrange deliveries and pickups with couriers.</li>\n  <li>Other duties as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proficient in basic office software and Google Workspace (Calendar, Drive, Doc, Sheet, Slides, etc).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now</strong> button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG JYA YEE (R23119014)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
